1
00:00:02,850 --> 00:00:07,370
<i>The first time I played </i>Fairies Story<i> 
was when I was in grade school.</i>

2
00:00:09,050 --> 00:00:12,280
<i>I was moved by the story and 
overwhelmed by the game world,</i>

3
00:00:12,870 --> 00:00:16,740
<i>but I especially grew fond 
of the beautiful characters.</i>

4
00:00:18,050 --> 00:00:22,310
<i>That's when I found out about 
the character designer job.</i>

5
00:00:18,620 --> 00:00:22,750
Character Designer:
Yagami Ko

6
00:00:23,530 --> 00:00:27,650
<i>The character designer of this 
game was called Yagami Ko.</i>

7
00:00:28,930 --> 00:00:30,190
<i>Yagami Ko.</i>

8
00:00:30,770 --> 00:00:32,610
<i>To me, that name...</i>

9
00:00:33,440 --> 00:00:35,330
<i>means something special!</i>

10
00:02:06,830 --> 00:02:08,680
<i>My name is Suzukaze Aoba.</i>

11
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:11,770
<i>I joined a game company one week ago.</i>

12
00:02:12,370 --> 00:02:14,410
<i>The name of the company is Eagle Jump.</i>

13
00:02:14,930 --> 00:02:20,180
<i>To my surprise, I was welcomed onto the 
team that's making </i>Fairies Story 3<i>!</i>

14
00:02:43,330 --> 00:02:44,890
Morning.

15
00:02:44,890 --> 00:02:46,560
Oh, good morning.

16
00:02:47,980 --> 00:02:52,090
<i>This lady who was sleeping under 
the desk is Yagami Ko-san.</i>

17
00:02:52,090 --> 00:02:55,820
<i>She's a hard worker, and it looks 
like she stayed the night at work.</i>

18
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,360
Character Designer:
Yagami Ko

19
00:02:56,880 --> 00:03:01,380
<i>I want to become a character 
designer like her one day.</i>

20
00:03:01,380 --> 00:03:03,580
<i>That's my current goal.</i>

21
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:06,120
<i>However...</i>

22
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:10,190
<i>I don't plan to sleep in 
my underwear like she does.</i>

23
00:03:10,190 --> 00:03:11,550
Stop staring.

24
00:03:11,550 --> 00:03:12,540
Ko-chan.

25
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,840
Don't be a bad example to other workers.

26
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,590
Whatever.

27
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,350
Good morning, Aoba-chan.

28
00:03:21,350 --> 00:03:23,390
Good morning to you, too!

29
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:26,330
<i>She's Toyama Rin-san, an art director.</i>

30
00:03:25,290 --> 00:03:27,060
Where're my pants?

31
00:03:26,330 --> 00:03:30,060
<i>An art director's job is to 
manage all the art related jobs.</i>

32
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:30,060
Goodness, clean this up.

33
00:03:31,830 --> 00:03:35,650
<i>Rin-san and Yagami-san joined at the 
same time and are close friends.</i>

34
00:03:32,290 --> 00:03:34,420
Can I toss these out?

35
00:03:34,420 --> 00:03:36,150
Oh, thanks.

36
00:03:36,150 --> 00:03:39,650
<i>I'm the only new employee this 
year, so I'm a little bit jealous.</i>

37
00:03:39,650 --> 00:03:42,150
Good morning!

38
00:03:42,550 --> 00:03:43,790
Aoba-chan, look.

39
00:03:43,790 --> 00:03:46,740
I got the new wand from <i>Moon Ranger</i>!

40
00:03:47,010 --> 00:03:49,000
Th-That's incredible.

41
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:51,750
There are twenty different 
quotes in this thing.

42
00:03:52,110 --> 00:03:55,850
It's so well designed and manufactured.

43
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:54,970
<i>She's Shinoda Hajime-san with the motion team.</i>

44
00:03:54,970 --> 00:03:57,100
<i>She sits right next to me.</i>

45
00:03:55,850 --> 00:03:58,670
It was super expensive, but totally worth!

46
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:58,670
<i>She's a super bright and energetic person.</i>

47
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:00,550
Good morning.

48
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:01,720
See this? When you swing it...

49
00:04:05,590 --> 00:04:06,240
Ow.

50
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:06,980
Oh, no!

51
00:04:06,980 --> 00:04:08,250
I'm sorry, Yun!

52
00:04:08,250 --> 00:04:09,350
Yun-san!

53
00:04:09,940 --> 00:04:11,160
<i>Iijima Yun-san.</i>

54
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,900
<i>She's on the character team with me.</i>

55
00:04:12,900 --> 00:04:16,590
<i>She joined with Hajime-san, and she's a 
responsible, older sister-like person.</i>

56
00:04:17,450 --> 00:04:19,370
Why're you getting so carried away 
at this time of morning?

57
00:04:19,370 --> 00:04:20,560
I'm sorry.

58
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,530
I got carried away.

59
00:04:23,580 --> 00:04:24,570
Oh!

60
00:04:25,850 --> 00:04:29,120
I'm getting the urge to swing it around, too.

61
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,400
Whoa, there.

62
00:04:32,810 --> 00:04:34,420
Good morning.

63
00:04:34,910 --> 00:04:36,860
Oh, good morning!

64
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:44,970
<i>She's Takimoto Hifumi-san, 
also on the character team.</i>

65
00:04:45,470 --> 00:04:48,130
<i>She joined before Hajime-san and Yun-san.</i>

66
00:04:48,130 --> 00:04:50,420
<i>She doesn't talk or smile much,</i>

67
00:04:50,420 --> 00:04:54,570
<i>but she's very nice and answers my 
questions through private messaging.</i>

